ust another inevitability. We must not avoid our destiny.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode047-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Uh-uhm, Kaoru-san. We have to take the pic-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode047-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"No one can resist the desire to experience the words of the great bard.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode047-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"Huh? I just...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"episode047-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Please, this way. I've decided that during my time in the theater club, I would take part in nothing other than the dramas of the great bard.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode047-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"Kaoru","body":"Of these collections of dramas and scripts, you are free to take as many as your heart desires. For I have committed them all to memory.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"episode047-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"Kanon","body":"All of them?! There are dozens of books here... You really do like his work.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":14,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timin